## ğŸ“Š Business Insights & Results

- **Medium Income Customers** hold the most deposits â€” lower risk, higher trust.
- **Accountants and Admins** had higher loan amounts and lower deposits â†’ possible red flags.
- **Foreign nationals** borrowed more but had shorter engagement â†’ monitor risk.
- **High Processing Fee** clients contributed significantly to total fee income.
- **Men spent more on credit**, but women saved more on average.

